      <title>印度调查发现流氓官员参与美国谋杀阴谋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/india-s-probe-finds-rogue-officials-involved-in-us-murder-plot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情高级官员透露，印度对美国声称在纽约企图谋杀一名锡克教领袖的事件进行调查后发现，未经政府授权的流氓特工参与了这一阴谋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/india-s-probe-finds-rogue-officials-involved-in-us-murder-plot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:13:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国海军舰艇在海上争端中尾随菲律宾海岸警卫队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/philippines-says-chinese-navy-ship-seen-circling-amid-sea-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾表示，一艘中国海军舰艇在前往菲律宾占领的南海岛屿的途中“尾随”其海岸警卫队船只，这是两国声称存在重叠海洋主张的最新事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/philippines-says-chinese-navy-ship-seen-circling-amid-sea-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 11:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南国家主席辞职，领导层出现新的动荡迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/vietnam-s-president-quits-in-latest-sign-of-leadership-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据越南共产党的一份声明，越南国家主席武文上于周三辞职，成为在对该国一些最高领导层调查范围扩大之际最新辞职的高级官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/vietnam-s-president-quits-in-latest-sign-of-leadership-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:12:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
